## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [CS24278]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;this mutation interferes with the interaction between HST and AtRAN1 in a yeast two hybrid assay; plants have slightly up-curled leaves and produce abaxial trichomes on leaf 3.
   - [CS24279]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;leaves up-rolled, precocious expression of adult traits, reduced leaf number, small root system, reduced fertility as both a male and female parent.
   - [CS24280]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;leaves up-rolled, precocious expression of adult traits, reduced leaf number, small root system, reduced fertility as both a male and female parent.
   - [CS3810]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;altered trichome distribution: precocious production of abaxial trichomes on rosette leaves, precocious loss of adaxial trichomes; leaves curled epinastically (spoon-shaped, concave); reduced leaf number per plant; small and semi-sterile flowers.
   - [CS3811]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;altered trichome distribution: precocious production of abaxial trichomes on rosette leaves (leaf 3), precocious loss of adaxial trichomes; leaves curled epinastically (spoon-shaped, concave); reduced leaf number per plant; small and semi-sterile flowers.
   - [hst]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Size reduction of roots and lateral organs of the shoot, delayed floral induction under short days, reduced fertility
